                  <li>
                    <a target='_blank' href="http://www.newsvine.com/_api/discuss?u=http://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2016-election/ted-cruz-tout-second-amendment-support-iowa-gun-range-n474431&h=Ted%20Cruz%3A%20&#x27;You%20Stop%20Bad%20Guys%20by%20Using%20Our%20Guns&#x27;&t=politics&cid=">
                      <i class="fa fa-comment-o" aria-hidden="true"></i><span class="social-list_txt">Comment</span>
                    </a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="ad-container ad-container_default ad-container_mobile ad-hide">
            <div class="ad-label ad-hide">
            	<a href="http://www.nbcnews.com/id/31066137/media-kit/" target="_blank">advertisement</a>
            </div>
            <div class="ad-content ad-xs boxflex" data-placement="boxflex"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="article_col-main article_col-main-left article_main">
              <div class="article-body" itemprop="articleBody">
                    <p> JOHNSTON, Iowa — Ted Cruz offered an impassioned defense of gun rights in the wake of the San Bernardino terrorist attack on Friday, telling a crowd at an Iowa gun range, &quot;you don't stop bad guys by taking away our guns, you stop bad guys by using our guns.&quot; </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> Cruz criticized the media for focusing on gun control in the wake of the shootings, telling his supporters: &quot;Folks in the media ask on behalf of Democrats, 'isn't it insensitive to do a Second Amendment rally after the shooting.' I really don't view our job as being sensitive to Islamic terrorists.&quot; </p>
                
              
              
              
                
              
              
              
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                    <div class="js-player-shell" data-playertype="Inline">
                      <div class="widget widget_video widget_trusted">
                          <div class="video-viewport">
